Hello World!

My website is currently evolving, and will be undergoing changes.

My name is Makayla Moster and I am a Ph.D. student studying Computer Science at Clemson University. In the summer of 2020, I joined the Human Factors Software Engineering (HFSE) lab under the guidance of Dr. Paige Rodeghero. I graduated from the University of North Carolina Wilmington with my B.S. with Honors in Computer Science in May 2019. In my free time, I am an avid reader, caretaker of my plethora of houseplants, and hobby crocheter.
